description: AMUNDI PRIME US TREASURY UCITS ETF DR seeks to replicate, as closely as possible, the performance of Solactive US Treasury Bond Index (Total return) whether it is rising or falling. This ETF offers exposure to USD-denominated securities issued by the United States of America Treasury and with maturity of at least 1 year. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus or www.solactive.com.
name: Amundi Prime US Treasury UCITS ETF DR (D)
